The paper deals with optimization problems involving submodular functions, which are commonly studied in the areas of algorithms, optimization, and game theory. Therefore, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are likely categories.
